Holwda ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how your personal information is collected, used, and disclosed by Holwda.

1. Information We Collect

Account Information: When you register, we collect your name, email address, and phone number.

Order & Delivery Data: We collect your delivery address and order history to process and deliver your sweets, cakes, and cafe orders.

Device Data: We may collect basic device information (OS version, device model) to improve app performance and troubleshoot errors.

2. How We Use Your Information

To process, fulfill, and track your orders.

To manage your account and provide customer support.

To send you order updates, receipts, and promotional offers (if consented).

To improve our app experience and security.

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell or rent your personal data. We only share information with third-party service providers (such as delivery drivers or payment gateways) strictly necessary to fulfill your orders.

4. Data Security & Retention
We implement appropriate technical security measures to protect your data. We retain your information for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide you services.

5. User Rights & Account Deletion
You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. You can request to delete your account and all associated data directly through the app settings or by contacting our support.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: support@holwda.com
